}

}

}


a{

}

#Navbar{
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;

}

.navbar{

    display: flex;
    width: 100%;
    /* padding-bottom: 10px; */
    box-shadow: 4px 4px rgb(149, 146, 146);
    /* background-color: hwb(300 17% 1% / 0.961); */

    /* position: fixed; */
}

.contact{
    position: absolute;
    padding: 25px;
    right: 10px;
    top:0px;
    /* texcolor: rgb(255, 38, 0); */
    
}

.contacts{

    color: #131111;

}

.contacts:hover{
    color: black;
    text-shadow: 10px;
    font-weight: bold;

}

.Login{

    font-size:large;
    font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
    font-weight: bold;
    background-color: rgb(42, 203, 239);
    border-radius:10px;
    border-color: rgb(126, 244, 58);

    bottom: 10px;
    
}

.Login:hover{

    font-weight: bolder;
    font-size: larger;

}

/* body */







.products-categories{
    
    display: flex;
    border: 29px;
